      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained by its previous owner. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts as it should, making it a reliable choice for daily driving. While the interior is clean and free of major wear, you may find a few minor cosmetic blemishes on the exterior consistent with regular use. It is a solid, dependable car that offers a great balance of performance and value without the premium price of a showroom model.",
