    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that's ready for its next adventure? This car has been so good to me! It runs like a dream and is super clean inside and out. It's been well-loved and is perfect for road trips or just zipping around town. I\u2019ve taken really solid care of it, so you\u2019re getting a fantastic vehicle at a sweet price. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 28900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
