      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission provides precise shifts, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery out of corners. The suspension remains taut, utilizing its original MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear configuration to deliver the tactile steering feedback this chassis is known for. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited use, the drivetrain and valvetrain are in excellent health, having recently undergone a valve clearance adjustment to factory specifications.",
